<Layout title="International Travel Guide" description="AIMS Travel — destination guides for international cultural travel: Africa safaris, Asia temples, European cities, the Americas, and the Middle East. Independent travel inspiration.">

  <div class="hero-band">
    <h1>AIMS Travel</h1>
    <p>Aiming to Make Your Travel Amazing</p>
  </div>

  <main>

    <img src="/images/home-hero.png" class="dest-hero-img" alt="Cinematic international travel scene — golden light, adventure, discovery" />

    <h1>Discover the World</h1>
    <p>
      There is no better investment than travel. Standing in the shadow of the Pyramids, watching a lion move through tall savanna grass at dawn, or turning a corner in Prague to find a medieval square unchanged for five centuries — these are moments that reframe how you understand the world and your place in it. AIMS Travel exists to help you plan, dream, and ultimately experience the international journeys that matter most.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our destination guides cover the world's most compelling regions for cultural and wildlife travel: East African safaris, the ancient civilizations of Asia, the imperial capitals of Europe, the lost cities of the Americas, and the storied landscapes of the Middle East. Whether you're planning a group journey or exploring independently, you'll find practical inspiration here for every kind of international traveler.
    </p>

    <div class="dest-grid">
      <a href="/destinations/africa" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Africa</h3>
        <p>South Africa, Kenya &amp; Tanzania, Botswana, Namibia</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/asia" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Asia &amp; the Orient</h3>
        <p>China &amp; Yangtze River, India, Vietnam &amp; Cambodia, Thailand</p>
      </a>
