        <h3>Europe</h3>
        <p>Greece, Central Europe, Italy, Scandinavia, Croatia</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/americas" class="dest-card">
        <h3>The Americas</h3>
        <p>Peru &amp; Machu Picchu, Ecuador &amp; Galapagos, Costa Rica, Cuba</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/middle-east" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Middle East</h3>
        <p>Egypt &amp; the Nile, Turkey, Israel</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations" class="dest-card">
        <h3>All Destinations</h3>
        <p>Browse every region and destination in our travel guide</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>How to Use This Guide</h3>
      <p>
        Each destination section covers the region's highlights in depth — what makes it worth the journey, the best time to go, how to get around, and where to stay. You'll find practical tips on navigating each destination alongside the kind of editorial context that helps you understand what you're looking at when you arrive. We link to hotels, cruise operators, and specialist travel providers we trust, so you can move from inspiration to booking without leaving the page.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Why Travel Internationally?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Broaden perspective</strong> — experiencing other cultures challenges assumptions and expands empathy in ways nothing else can</li>
      <li><strong>Witness history in context</strong> — seeing the Colosseum, the Taj Mahal, or the temples of Angkor in person transforms how you understand the past</li>
      <li><strong>Wildlife encounters</strong> — Africa's national parks offer wildlife viewing on a scale impossible to replicate anywhere else on earth</li>
      <li><strong>Culinary discovery</strong> — every great region has a food culture worth traveling for: Sichuan, Oaxacan, Turkish, Vietnamese</li>
      <li><strong>Connection</strong> — group travel and guided journeys create friendships among like-minded explorers that often last a lifetime</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin-top:2rem"><a href="/destinations">Explore all destinations &rarr;</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="/about">About AIMS Travel &rarr;</a></p>
